            <div type="section" xml:id="Legislation">
                <head>Legislation</head>
                <p>There is no official legislation governing access to diplomatic archives.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="section" xml:id="Location">
                <head>Location</head>
                <p>National Archives: BP 7030, Présidence du Faso, Ouagadougou.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="section" xml:id="Procedures">
                <head> Procedures</head>
                <p>Researchers should contact the nearest embassy of Burkina Faso to inquire about
                    the feasibility of research and location of relevant diplomatic records. </p>
            </div>
